The templateXValue[5] calendar lasts for approximately 365.24 days ; this means that most years have 365 days , with one extra day being added every fourth templateYLabel[1] , unless the templateYLabel[1] is divisible by 100 but not 400 ( for example , the templateYLabel[1] 2000 was a leap templateYLabel[1] , whereas 2100 and 2200 will not be ) .
